name: Speed Dungeon
description:
Hello my name is Sebastian AKA: sebbsubb.

This game is made for the QaziJam 5.

This was my first ever game jam that i participated in. I am quite happy with the results. Feel free to drop a comment what you think about the game!

The QaziJam 5 was a 5 day long Game jam where i had the themes:
* Cat.
* Pixel knife.

I made everything by myself, textures codes etc. NOTE: Except stuff i wrote in the credits. Thanks so much to those who helped me and believed in me!

For more information about the game read the README file in the game folder! Thanks!
